}
!}
go-to: chancellor_negotiation_spd

# ============================================
# CHANCELLOR NEGOTIATION - SPD IN GOVERNMENT
# ============================================

@chancellor_negotiation_spd

= Chancellor Negotiations - [+ coalition_name +]

**Coalition Partners:**

[+ coalition_partners_list +]

**The coalition must now select a Chancellor.**

**Candidates:**

[+ chancellor_candidates_display +]

[? if spd_chancellor_preference = "mueller" : The SPD has put forward Hermann Müller as their preferred candidate. ?]
[? if spd_chancellor_preference = "wels" : The SPD has put forward Otto Wels as their preferred candidate. ?]
[? if spd_chancellor_preference = "braun" : The SPD has put forward Otto Braun as their preferred candidate. ?]
[? if spd_chancellor_preference = "hilferding" : The SPD has put forward Rudolf Hilferding as their preferred candidate. ?]

[? if president = "Hindenburg" and year >= 1930 : **Note:** President Hindenburg has expressed strong preferences about who should lead the government. Choosing a Chancellor he opposes may create difficulties. ?]

[? if president = "Hindenburg" and year >= 1932 and candidate_0_party = "SPD" : **Warning:** Hindenburg has made it clear he will not accept an SPD Chancellor under current circumstances. ?]

**Who should become Chancellor?**

- @choose_chancellor_1: Support [+ candidate_0_name +] ([+ candidate_0_party +])
- @choose_chancellor_2: Support [+ candidate_1_name +] ([+ candidate_1_party +])
- @choose_chancellor_3: Support [+ candidate_2_name +] ([+ candidate_2_party +])
- @choose_chancellor_4: Support [+ candidate_3_name +] ([+ candidate_3_party +])
- @choose_chancellor_5: Support [+ candidate_4_name +] ([+ candidate_4_party +])
- @choose_chancellor_6: Support [+ candidate_5_name +] ([+ candidate_5_party +])

